imdb.plot outline: Jo Wemple hosts a behind the scenes Travel Guide to California's Central Coast - San Luis Obispo County. A perfect show to help travelers plan their next journey, Jo speaks with Celebrity Chefs, Wine Makers, and Artists as she explores the best of the best that the county has to offer.
